cn.inbot.padbotsdk.listener

Interface RobotScanListener


  • public interface RobotScanListener

    Robot Scanning Listener

    Listen to using the Bluetooth search robot. By implementing and setting this listener, the methods in this interface will be invoked when scanning robot.

    Author : Inbot
    Create Date : 2017/5/11
    JDK version used : JDK1.8
    Version : V3.0.0
